Wednesday, April 24, 1996

MERIT DOCKET

95-2359. W.W. Williams Co. v. Medina Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 94-H-669. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents.
